{"tid":827850,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"又中！沈大師：短線反彈浪未完！","createTime":"2018-09-19T08:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T10:06:40.000Z","uid":43261,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"86ed1ed96bfbf6e1709c78c144ed7aa5c210cde3","tid":827850,"uid":43261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:35:17.000Z","msg":"訊匯證券行政總裁沈振盈，今接受本報訪問時表示，港股於28000點有阻力，因此市場正進行正常調整，「不過，短線反彈浪未完！」他解釋，上星期港股一連幾日弱勢，更失27000，不過當時期指低水情況收窄；同時，期指倉先減後加，似係反咗手；第三是，那幾天成交金額夠大，過千億成交。「通當咁恐慌嘅時間，過千億肯定係大戶買，散戶沽。嗰日做到咁恐慌情況都咁大成交，跟住期指低水收窄，期指大成交，仲要之前兩日減完先再加，咁呢啲似係轉咗手做好倉主導。」他預期，下月期指可望於28000點以上結算。<br />\n<br />\n策略方面，「騰訊（700）來到呢啲位，上面我就睇375元。」短線若回落至350元或以下，可以買入博反彈。若騰訊未能跌至此水平，水位唔夠，「咁就集中火力睇港交所（388），因為如果上28000，港交所會飆一浸上去。如果呢一浸上去，我估計港交所就235蚊左右。」<br />\n<br />\n23-8-2018<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/163336_af24a33c55bb99516eb0fe7aef05e459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F163336_af24a33c55bb99516eb0fe7aef05e459.jpg&h=2d50d41e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f9da2756d1f309588a2fb524c9231f65a164db8","tid":827850,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92030fede6db07572307b16007b92cc462fe3e8","tid":827850,"uid":137493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T08:47:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcd38be6fea282eb560076d3449c3d97db0937f","tid":827850,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"就快期結，收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d81bf5f8699b0d523e6af1b4ed4e9bb596594d","tid":827850,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">23-8-2018</span></span>"},{"pid":"9241afea2657befc425cbc71e04393e25b790577","tid":827850,"uid":166462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3d81bf5f8699b0d523e6af1b4ed4e9bb596594d","tid":827850,"uid":70888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:30:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">23-8-2018</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T10:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}